<p style="mso-list:l2 level1 lfo122;page-break-after:auto" class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><a name="_9f019144-5588-4436-ffdd-36e8dd4425da" id="_9f019144-5588-4436-ffdd-36e8dd4425da"></a>Professional ethics relating to commercial and government projects
</p>
